  "local_port": 45960,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What companies are similar to IDEO in Paris?",
  "response": "If you're looking for companies in Paris that offer services similar to IDEO\u2014focusing on design thinking, innovation, user experience, and creative problem-solving\u2014here are several notable firms to consider:\n\n1. **Designit (A Wipro Company)**\n   - **Website:** [designit.com](https://www.designit.com/)\n   - **Overview:** A global strategic design firm specializing in customer experience, innovation, and service design. Designit collaborates with clients across various industries to develop innovative solutions and enhance user experiences.\n\n2. **Fjord (Part of Accenture Interactive)**\n   - **Website:** [fjord.com](https://www.fjord.com/)\n   - **Overview:** Fjord is a design and innovation consultancy within Accenture Interactive, focusing on service design and user-centered innovation. They work on creating impactful experiences across digital and physical platforms.\n\n3. **Frog Design**\n   - **Website:** [frogdesign.com](https://www.frogdesign.com/)\n   - **Overview:** Frog is a global design and strategy firm known for its work in product design, digital transformation, and innovation consulting. They partner with clients to create user-centric products and services.\n\n4. **FABERNOVEL**\n   - **Website:** [faber-innov.com](https://www.faber-innov.com/)\n   - **Overview:** A French consulting group specializing in digital innovation, strategy, and transformation. FABERNOVEL assists organizations in developing innovative business models and leveraging new technologies.\n\n5. **Studio Ozzie**\n   - **Website:** [studioozzie.com](https://www.studioozzie.com/)\n   - **Overview:** A Paris-based design consultancy that focuses on user experience, interaction design, and design thinking. Studio Ozzie works with clients to create intuitive and engaging digital products.\n\n6. **Artefact**\n   - **Website:** [artefact.com](https://www.artefact.com/)\n   - **Overview:** A digital design and innovation agency that combines technology, design, and strategy to help businesses transform and innovate. Artefact emphasizes data-driven design solutions.\n\n7. **Ekino**\n   - **Website:** [ekino.com](https://www.ekino.com/)\n   - **Overview:** A French digital services agency offering solutions in digital transformation, innovation, and design. Ekino works on web development, mobile applications, and user experience design.\n\n8. **DeepSIX**\n   - **Website:** [deepsix.com](https://www.deepsix.com/)\n   - **Overview:** A Paris-based innovation and design consultancy specializing in collaborative design processes, workshops, and strategic innovation projects to drive business growth.\n\n9. **Uzik**\n   - **Website:** [uzik.fr](https://www.uzik.fr/) *(Please verify as URLs may change)*\n   - **Overview:** A digital transformation and design consultancy focusing on creating innovative digital products and services. Uzik emphasizes user-centric approaches and agile methodologies.\n\n10. **UX-Republic**\n    - **Website:** [ux-republic.com](https://www.ux-republic.com/)\n    - **Overview:** Specializes in user experience (UX) design, usability testing, and design thinking workshops. UX-Republic helps organizations enhance their digital products through improved user experiences.\n\n11. **Essential Studio**\n    - **Website:** [essential-studio.com](https://www.essential-studio.com/)\n    - **Overview:** A design and innovation agency based in Paris, focusing on brand strategy, product design, and creative consulting to help businesses innovate and differentiate themselves in the market.\n\n12. **Kea & Partners**\n    - **Website:** [kea-partners.com](https://www.kea-partners.com/)\n    - **Overview:** A strategy consulting firm with expertise in innovation, digital transformation, and design strategy. Kea & Partners assists clients in developing forward-thinking strategies and innovative solutions.\n\nThese firms offer a range of services that align closely with IDEO\u2019s approach to design and innovation. Depending on your specific needs\u2014whether it's product design, service design, digital transformation, or strategic innovation\u2014you may find the right partner among these Paris-based companies.",
